file.name: templated-server-example.oas3.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.0
paths:
  "/pet":
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: test
servers:
- url: "{schema}://{host}/{basePath}"
  variables:
    schema:
      default: http
      enum:
      - http
      - https
    host:
      default: stoplight.io
      enum:
      - stoplight.io
      - dev.stoplight.io
    basePath:
      default: api
